</taxonomicName>
is a widely distributed species in 
<collectingCountry box="[1021,1091,524,550]" name="China" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">China</collectingCountry>
(Sichuan, Shaanxi, Hubei, Yunnan).
</paragraph>
